<div id="Idea_2912"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2912-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2912">Ability to vote "No" against a candidate.&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/4129-4049">bobhilt1</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">8 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">A "No" vote against a candidate would offset a vote for the candidate.  The candidate with the most net votes would win.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2912" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2912', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2242&topicID=2912')">Comments (4)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2912"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2242">New Strategies and Techniques</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=voting">voting</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2912"></div>
